Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sports Heroes: Dunk for Victories
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi joins the team
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode, we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats finally got Blazey as their coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Blazey and Slowy have a lingering grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats accidentally discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy a few years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A video left for them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This video
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey and Slowy reconciled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to reach the pinnacle of a goat’s life?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you join the Goat Basketball Team and win the championship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:00:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No need, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning the championship would be beneficial, so who would participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your methods for recruiting new team members
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s really ineffective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,village head…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and see, you’ve successfully joined the Goat Basketball Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You will receive these gifts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to join the Goat Basketball Team…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A goat that only seeks profit, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t cause trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to pass two tests to join the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The first test is a physical fitness test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It must pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then can you participate in the second round of shooting tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is leaving so troublesome? Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The gifts seem quite plentiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let’s register.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have registered, come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My great-aunt’s latest golden cake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, I want to play basketball too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let’s begin the physical fitness test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,First is the strength test
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This test is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go lift your own dumbbells.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi failed the strength test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the running test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they running so slowly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the one who’s slow; they’ve all crossed the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi also failed the physical fitness test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter, there are other tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Failed the jumping test
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jonie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This type of test is too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not have an eating contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure I’ll pass this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, you really need to work out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single item passed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I destined to never have a golden cake in this lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to wait for me, you delicious golden cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely eat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, please give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The coach is very strict
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I give you another chance so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come back and test again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They actually agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have seen his persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why I gave him a chance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, he can channel that same dedication into basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Want us to help train you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can do it no matter how I train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, I absolutely must eat the golden cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what your reason is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you make the team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our three grassland musketeers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can play ball together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we are all beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The training methods may be unprofessional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, you definitely won’t be worse than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn’t seem like something to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go train right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Training begins…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven’t even started, and you’re already hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s eat something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be better if you ate while training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really possible to eat and train at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, what do you mean by saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll find out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat it once you catch up with the toy car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanted to turn Paddi’s appetite into motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s try other methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To successfully perform a pull-up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then can you eat bread
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Paddi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems our training methods are effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This will incentivize Paddi to do it more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the trick to this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep training
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi is rarely seen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you persist in doing one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He really doesn’t look like him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I think about what he did…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for eating cake…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what our Paddi should be like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, we’ll run with you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grassland Trio, chasing their basketball dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,come on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s for the cake
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,nice shot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing, I’m just a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi has tried his best to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can pass the physical fitness test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My golden cake, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let’s start the test now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,one time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Two times
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, much better than last time, just a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will definitely pass the second running test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no snacks in front this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absolutely no motivation to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re almost at the finish line, just hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s cheer for the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, there’s still a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, you’ve improved a lot this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Paddi, you’ve done a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Show me the grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad test
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going home to eat snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shoot free throws and make five out of ten…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll make an exception and let you join the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, Paddi is a beginner in basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you possibly make the shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll try anything as long as there’s a chance to eat cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It really didn’t work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there’s little hope left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it’s for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what it feels like. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Another shot made! Paddi is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, an outsider
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has such a great feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he is trained properly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will definitely become a team
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,An indispensable member
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The team is indispensable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One member?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, how did you make that shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know either, because I was just so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I mistook the basketball hoop for a winter swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of basketballs as chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pour chocolate over the tomato sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It will definitely taste delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of Paddi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely passable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on joining the basketball team!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s eat cake together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,good…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These cakes are the result of your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to share some with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your help in training me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t get the cake either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And cake tastes better when everyone shares it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, Paddi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is no cake as a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still play basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, I can try playing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And win the championship later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would wish for an endless supply of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I’m going to see Tibbie soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s not even home, what is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know either, maybe she’s busy with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(to be continued)
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
